Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_tx_pause_pkt_type

AGL_GMX_TX_PAUSE_PKT_TYPE = Packet TX Pause Packet TYPE field

Notes: Additionally reset when both MIX0/1_CTL[RESET] are set to 1.
